d and Emotions</b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">If it is time for a positive change in your life, emWave2 will help. This unique training system helps you learn to build inner resilience — a state of poise and readiness for effectively dealing with stressful feelings and whatever challenges come your way. In only five to ten minutes of practice a day, emWave2 can bring more mental and emotional ease and flexibility into your life.  emWave2 users notice transformations in attitudes, emotions and perspectives as they become more positive and resilient with this easy-to-use technology.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>New and Versatile </b>—<b> On The Go or at Your Computer</b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">The new emWave2 combines the portability of the original handheld emWave, which provides input via lights and sound, with a rich graphical  interface which displays on your computer. Use it on the go, or at home or work — just plug into your computer to download and review previous sessions, run a new session with the real-time heart rhythm display, or play one of the interactive coherence-building games.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\"><b></b><span class=\"s1\"><b>The Coherence Breakthrough</b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">emWave2 technology is based on “the coherence breakthrough”. Coherence is a state of synchronization between your heart, brain and autonomic nervous system which has been proven to have numerous mental, emotional and physical benefits. You can think of coherence as a simultaneous state of relaxation, readiness and revitalization. It’s a first step in prepping for what athletes call “the zone”. Coherence improves performance, health and emotional well-being and overall life resiliency.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p5\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Typical Benefits that People Notice</b></span><span class=\"s2\"><b>\r\n</b></span><span class=\"s1\"><b>With 2 Weeks of Genuine Practice:</b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\r\n	<li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s1\">More calm</span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s1\">Better sleep</span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s1\">Less reactivity</span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s1\">Less worry</span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s1\">More alertness</span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s1\">Better focus and decision making</span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s1\">More positive attitudes</span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s1\">More ease and  inner peace</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>How it works</b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">The emWave2 is an advanced heart rate monitor, able to measure subtle changes in your heart rhythms. This type of measurement is known as heart rate variability analysis or HRV. The analysis of HRV is a noninvasive measurement that reflects heart-brain interaction and autonomic nervous system dynamics, which are particularly sensitive to changes in your emotional state.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Heart Rhythms and Coherence </b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">When you experience stressful emotions such as tension, anxiety, irritation, or anger, your heart-rhythm pattern becomes irregular and incoherent, negatively affecting your health, brain function, performance and sense of well-being. When you experience positive emotions such as appreciation, care, joy and love, your heart-rhythm pattern is more ordered and coherent.</span></p>','emWave Flow Monitoring System, Handheld','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">De-Stress and perform by getting into the “flow” state</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The emWave Pro is a scientifically validated heart-rate monitoring system that facilitates learning techniques to create an optimal state in which the heart, mind and emotions are operating in-sync and balanced.  This coherent state builds resilience, decreases stress, increases energy, and promotes focus, mental clarity and emotional balance.</span></p>','publish','open','closed','','emwave-flow-monitor-handheld','','','2015-07-27 12:14:54','2015-07-27 18:14:54','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/product/emwave-flow-monitor-handheld/',0,'product','',0),(148,3,'2015-07-07 00:42:00','2015-07-07 06:42:00','[et_pb_section][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\n<h1 class=\"h1\">Time Keeps on Slippin\'</h1>\n<p class=\"p1\">In your time, yes, but nowadays shut up! Besides, these are adult stemcells, harvested from perfectly healthy adults whom I killed for their stemcells. Bite my shiny metal ass. Shut up and take my money!</p>\n\n<h2 class=\"h2\">The Why of Fry</h2>\n<p class=\"p1\">No! The cat shelter\'s on to me. I don\'t \'need\' to drink. I can quit anytime I want! It\'s just like the story of the grasshopper and the octopus. All year long, the grasshopper kept burying acorns for winter, while the octopus mooched off his girlfriend and watched TV. But then the winter came, and the grasshopper died, and the octopus ate all his acorns. Also he got a race car. Is any of this getting through to you?</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Ow, my spirit!</li>\n	<li>You guys realize you live in a sewer, right?</li>\n	<li>Kids have names?</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 class=\"h3\">Raging Bender</h3>\n<p class=\"p1\">I\'ll get my kit! Oh, I always feared he might run off like this. Why, why, why didn\'t I break his legs? Yes. You gave me a dollar and some candy. As an interesting side note, as a head without a body, I envy the dead.</p>\n\n<h4 class=\"h4\">Bendless Love</h4>\n<p class=\"p1\">So I really am important? How I feel when I\'m drunk is correct? Um, is this the boring, peaceful kind of taking to the streets? Tell them I hate them. I guess if you want children beaten, you have to do it yourself. There\'s one way and only one way to determine if an animal is intelligent. Dissect its brain!</p>\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]','Faculty','','publish','open','open','','faculty','','','2015-07-07 00:42:00','2015-07-07 06:42:00','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=148',2,'page','',0),(150,3,'2015-07-07 00:45:25','2015-07-07 06:45:25','[et_pb_section][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_sidebar admin_label=\"Sidebar\" orientation=\"left\" area=\"et_pb_widget_area_1\" background_layout=\"light\" remove_border=\"off\" /][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"2_3\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\n<h2 class=\"h2\">Julie Hutchinson</h2>\n<h3 class=\"h3\">Management Consultant and Founder of Core Performance &amp; Chocolate Shaman</h3>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Julie Hutchinson is a dynamic leadership trainer, sales and management consultant, and Founder of Core Performance, LLC. Julie has devoted her career to coaching various organizations, including the U.S. military, to achieve maximum performance or “Coherence” using innovative biofeedback tools and real-time analytic feedback mechanism.  Julie is also the founder of <a href=\"http://chocolateshaman.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"s2\">Chocolate Shaman</span></a>, an organization devoted to teaching the world about the numerous health benefits of chocolate.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Julie’s Coherence workshops deliver quantitative, science-based techniques to develop concentration, deliver stress relief, and improve productivity and performance. Julie has helped both private corporations as well as thousands of members in the U.S. Armed Forces to learn and activate this science-based technology to self-regulate and build energy and resilience.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Additionally, after experiencing the healing power of raw foods in her own life and becoming a Level 2 certified raw foods instructor, Julie started <a href=\"http://chocolateshaman.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"s2\">Chocolate Shaman</span></a>, a company providing pure, organic cacao direct from growers in South America, to share the natural health benefits of chocolate with the world.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Inspired by a trip deep into the Peruvian Amazon Jungle, Julie takes you on a journey into the history of Chocolate, including how it was discovered, how it is grown, and shares the secrets and magical journey of this amazing food.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Julie combines business acumen with a passion for exploring personal development. She has studied with noted teachers in yoga, Qi Gong, meditation and human consciousness. She is a certified HeartMath coach, Core Language instructor, certified yoga instructor and a lifelong athlete with numerous extreme sport accomplishments.</span></p>\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\n\nA dynamic leadership trainer, Julie Hutchinson has devoted her career to coaching various organizations in achieving maximum performance and Brain/Heart Coherence using innovative biofeedback tools and real-time analytic feedback mechanisms.  Julie\'s Coherence workshops deliver quantitative, science-based techniques to develop concentration, deliver stress relief, and improve productivity and performance.  Her methodology has helped private corporations as well as thousands of members in the U.S. Armed Forces to learn and activate this technology to self-regulate and build energy and resilience.  Julie\'s science-based approach uses an immediate tool that is particularly helpful for individuals suffering from post-traumatic stress disorders, anxiety, depression, OCD and ADHD.\n\nJulie\'s organization, Chocolate Shaman, is devoted to educating the world on the myriad health benefits of high quality chocolate.  Her company provides pure, organic cacao directly from South American farmers and values the process of educating people across the globe on the healing power of raw foods.  Inspired by an exploration of the Peruvian Amazon Jungle, Julie takes you on a journey into the history of chocolate, including how it was discovered, how it is grown and harvested, as well as the secret healing properties of this amazing food.\n\nCombining business acumen with a deep passion for continued positive personal development, Julie believes in the knowledge she has gained through study with noted teachers in the traditions of yoga, qi gong, meditation and human consciousness.  Julie is a certified HeartMath Coach, Core Language Instructor, Certified Yoga Teacher 300hr, Level II Certified Raw Foods Instructor and a lifelong athlete with numerous extreme sport accomplishments.\n\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]','Julie Hutchinson','','publish','open','open','','julie-hutchinson','','','2015-07-07 00:45:25','2015-07-07 06:45:25','',148,'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=150',0,'page','',0),(168,3,'2015-07-07 01:39:03','2015-07-07 07:39:03','[et_pb_section][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n<h2 class=\"h2\">Resilience and You</h2>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">There are four foundational elements in the resilience equation: Mind, Body, Spirit, and Social. To be wholly resilient, we must diligently attend to each of these aspects in our lives.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"h2\">What Is Resilience?</h2>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">Are you resilient? Resilience is defined as the capacity to prepare for, recover from, and adapt to the constant challenges that we face every day.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">To live a resilient lifestyle and maximize your full human potential, it is essential to develop the four elements of your personal ecosystem: Mind, Body, Spirit, and Social. Ultimately, balancing these elements is key to unlocking your personal resilience.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">Resilience also relates to efficiently optimizing your personal inner energy resources. How much resilience capacity do you store in your “internal battery”?</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">The Resilient1 helps you builds your resilience holistically from all four domains by providing the purest, time-tested solutions for the modern high performer.</p>\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][et_pb_image admin_label=\"Image\" src=\"http://resilient1.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/dimensions.svg\" show_in_lightbox=\"off\" url_new_window=\"off\" animation=\"off\" sticky=\"off\" align=\"left\" force_fullwidth=\"off\" always_center_on_mobile=\"on\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"] [/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n<h2 class=\"h2\">Individual Excellence</h2>\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_image admin_label=\"Image\" src=\"http://resilient1.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/IMG_7185.jpg\" show_in_lightbox=\"off\" url_new_window=\"off\" animation=\"off\" sticky=\"off\" align=\"left\" force_fullwidth=\"off\" always_center_on_mobile=\"on\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"] [/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"2_3\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n<p class=\"p1\">The increasing complexity of the world we live in creates unnecessary stress and distraction. As we navigate our personal wellbeing, this hollow, monotonous grind can often lead us down an unfulfilled, unhealthy path. And as stress builds, we search for solutions to help us better manage the complexity of our life. Solving for the whole person is an equation that must encompass body, mind, and spirit to build a foundation for longevity and wellness.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">The expert faculty at Resilient1 has developed and curated the finest tools, services and products to help you uncover individual excellence: your true potential, a life you hope for, a life better than the one you know today.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><b>Gain perspective</b> – experience ground-breaking techniques that build capacity and clarity</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><b>Reduce Stress</b> – master the art of mediation, coherence training, and other techniques to effectively manage stress</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><b>Control Wellness</b> – learn holistic methods of preventative and curative health management using diet, exercise, and intention</p>\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n<h2 class=\"h2\">Professional Excellence</h2>\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"2_3\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n<p class=\"p1\">The 24×7 global workplace requires leaders who deliver sustained performance under unrelenting pressure and change. Executives must deliver sustained performance far in excess of professional athletes, including controlling emotional response and producing environments that empower both the individual and the organization.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">Our faculty experts have sustained decades of excellence in numerous business industries, honing the essential tools that deliver holistic performance in our ever-changing work environment. By maximizing your potential using these tools, you and those you lead will thrive under the pressure of constant change. With Resilient1, you can:</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><b>Embody Leadership</b> – engage, develop, and inspire others to greater levels of performance, collaboration and engagement</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><b>Master Communication</b> – develop environments and employees that sustain meaningful and rewarding work</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><b>Reduce Stress</b> – master the art of mediation, coherence training, and other specialized techniques that attack tension and anxiety and develop resilience</p>\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_image admin_label=\"Image\" src=\"http://resilient1.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/IMG_1506.jpg\" show_in_lightbox=\"off\" url_new_window=\"off\" animation=\"off\" sticky=\"off\" align=\"left\" force_fullwidth=\"off\" always_center_on_mobile=\"on\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"] [/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]','Resilience and You','','publish','open','open','','resilience-and-you','','','2015-07-27 12:19:24','2015-07-27 18:19:24','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=168',3,'page','',0),(170,3,'2015-07-07 01:39:49','2015-07-07 07:39:49','[et_pb_section][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n<h2 class=\"h2\">Philosophy</h2>\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"2_3\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" backgr